<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天晚上，森林里特别温暖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>月光明亮，照进狼洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸休息一整天后醒过来，打了个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈躺在近处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把鼻子放在滚来滚去叫个不停的四只狼宝宝身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸伸了个懒腰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼妈妈，又该去打猎了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，洞口出现一个影子，长着一条毛茸茸的尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是豺狼塔巴其。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>塔巴其总是要吃的，所以狼爸爸和狼妈妈很讨厌他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也很怕塔巴其，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为塔巴其又狡猾，又脾气坏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候，他会疯狂地在森林里跑，看见什么就咬什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当塔巴其发疯的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>甚至连凶恶的老虎谢尔坎也离他远远的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我肚子饿。”塔巴其说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你进来看看吧，塔巴其。”狼爸爸叹了口气说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我可以向你保证，这里没有食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也许能找点吃的。”塔巴其回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他慢慢地朝洞里面走去，用鼻子到处闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就发现了一根放了很久的骨头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面有一点肉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你的食物，很好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>塔巴其说，舔了舔嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他盯着小小的狼宝宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎哟，你的孩子们真好看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈走近孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和狼爸爸对视了一眼，显得很不安。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，还有......”塔巴其继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎发现了几个新的打猎地点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉我他会暂时在这里打猎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这里？”狼妈妈惊讶地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，他没有权利在这里打猎！”狼爸爸大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎必须呆在河边，那是森林法则！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>塔巴其笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要不要我告诉他你在担心什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出去！”狼爸爸厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去跟你的主人打猎吧，塔巴其，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你折磨了我们一个晚上，够了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会走的。”塔巴其平静地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，别忘了谢尔坎的新打猎地点，我警告过你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其实，你现在就能听见他的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在下面的灌木里打猎呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>塔巴其走后，狼爸爸走出了洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他真的听见下面山谷里传来老虎的低吼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈走出来，站在他旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来谢尔坎今晚不会吃动物，我觉得他会吃人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸龇了龇白白的牙齿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林里瓢虫和青蛙那么多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎为什么非得吃人呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林里有一条重要法则——动物不可以吃人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎的吼声越来越大，突然，传来了哭声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸和狼妈妈听得见谢尔坎在灌木丛里痛苦地滚来滚去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他疼哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只傻老虎可能跑进了人类的篝火，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听上去他的脚好像被火烫了。”狼爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈动了动一只耳朵，仔细地听着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像有什么东西往山顶跑呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>附近的灌木沙沙响了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸放低身子准备出击。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，突然，狼妈妈惊讶地倒吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是个人类宝宝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小男孩儿站在狼爸爸和狼妈妈面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个小人类看着狼爸爸的脸，眨了眨眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼爸爸！”狼妈妈小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快！把这小男孩儿弄到我们洞里去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸走上前，轻轻地叼住了小男孩儿的脖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，把小男孩儿叼进洞里放在了狼宝宝们旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>